<%- include('partials/head', { title: user.role === 'admin' ? 'Admin Guide' : 'Moderator Guide' }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-6">
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6">

    <div class="mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1"><%= user.role === 'admin' ? 'Admin Guide' : 'Moderator Guide' %></h1>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Your role on Family News</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">You have a few extra tools to help keep things welcoming and organized. Use them with good judgment — and know that everything deleted can be restored for up to 2 weeks.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5">

      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">📌 Pinning posts</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Use the pin icon on any post to keep it at the top of the feed. Great for important announcements or a post everyone should see. Tap the pin again to unpin.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">📣 Big News</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Mark any post as Big News to give it a banner and send a family-wide notification (push + email). Use this for things the whole family should know about. Tap again to unmark.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">✕ Removing posts &amp; comments</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">You can delete any post or comment — not just your own. Deleted items go to the trash and can be restored within 2 weeks. Use this carefully; members can always remove their own posts themselves.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">🔗 Invite links</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Create invite links to bring new family members onto the site. Open invites work for up to 50 people over 2 days — great for sharing broadly. Single-use invites are good for one specific person and last 7 days.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">🗑️ Trash &amp; restore</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">The <a href="/mod" class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 font-medium hover:underline">Mod panel</a> shows everything that's been deleted in the last 2 weeks. You can restore anything there, or permanently delete it early if needed.</p>
      </div>

      <% if (user.role === 'admin') { %>
      <div class="border-l-4 border-brand-600 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">👥 User management</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">The <a href="/admin" class="text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 font-medium hover:underline">Admin panel</a> lets you manage user accounts, assign roles, send password resets, and update email addresses.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-brand-600 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">📅 Birthday &amp; anniversary events</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Add birthdays and anniversaries to the shared calendar from the admin panel. Events post automatically at 8am on the day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-brand-600 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">📊 Analytics &amp; read receipts</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Post detail pages show how many members have seen each post. Full usage analytics are available from the admin panel.</p>
      </div>
      <% } else { %>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/40 rounded-xl p-4 mt-2">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Admin-only</p>
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">👥 Manage user accounts and roles</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">📅 Add birthday &amp; anniversary events</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">📊 Full analytics and site settings</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% } %>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body></html>
